<div id="events-vs-conversions-modal"
     data-controller="modal"
     class="hidden fixed inset-0 z-50">
  <div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/50" data-action="click->modal#close"></div>

  <div class="fixed inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl max-w-2xl w-full p-6 max-h-[80vh] overflow-y-auto">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Events vs Conversions</h3>
        <button type="button" data-action="click->modal#close" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Events</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-3">
            Actions <strong>on the way to</strong> a conversion. Mid-funnel engagement signals.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>Form views</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>CTA clicks</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>Video plays</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>Scroll depth</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>Pricing page visits</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-indigo-200 rounded-lg p-4 bg-indigo-50/30">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 rounded flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Conversions</h4>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-3">
            Goals that trigger <strong>multi-touch attribution</strong>. The actions that matter most.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-400"></span>Purchases</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-400"></span>Lead form submissions</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-400"></span>Demo bookings</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-400"></span>Signups / trial starts</div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-400"></span>Phone calls (click-to-call)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-3 text-xs text-gray-600">
        <strong>Rule of thumb:</strong> If you'd assign a dollar value to it, it's a conversion. Everything else is an event.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
